songs.title: Swag So Official
songs.lyrics:

Super fresh
And my swag so official
And my swag so official
Swag swag so official
And my swag so official
Swag swag so official

The world turns

So look learn
All I need's my cake

Then I'm straight like a good perm
And her swag so official
Taylor made money gang
I'm the general

Chorus

Verse 2:
